  <div style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1.4px;color:#005EB8;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;">Lane synthesis &middot; what is happening across the actors</div>
  <div style="font-size:13.5px;color:#212B32;line-height:1.7;">A supplier admitted to the framework can be called off by any commissioner without being re-assured each time. That is the speed multiplier the model exists to create. The supplier&apos;s clinical safety case and lab assurance both travel with the admission; the framework administrator runs the cycle from admission inquiry through to live. The bottleneck the lane exposes is administrative capacity, not assurance quality &mdash; suppliers wait on the framework, not on safety reviews.</div>
</div>
<!-- ==================== LANE 3: SERVICE DELIVERY ==================== -->
<div class="swimlane-section" id="lane-2">
<div class="sl-card">
<div class="sl-head">
<h3>3. Service delivery</h3>
<p>How a patient gets a test, takes it, and gets a clear result: whichever way the test was initiated. <strong>Joe (supplier)</strong> dispatches the kit and runs (or routes) the lab. <strong>Priya (NHSE Platform)</strong> hosts the ordering surface and carries the result back. The configuration-specific clinician (<strong><span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">Adam</span></strong> for <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">PSA-AS</span>, <strong><span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">Hannah</span></strong> for <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">iron deficiency anaemia</span>, TBC for HIV-LA and PSA-AS monitoring-gap) initiates the order where applicable and reads the result. <strong>Aisha (Clinical / CSG)</strong> handles the reactive path. The lane shows what is universal (foundation) and what varies by configuration (overlay), with three named examples: <strong><span class="cfg-mark" data-config="hiv">Abdul</span></strong> (CVKM screening, <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="hiv">Self-init</span>), <strong><span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">Mark</span></strong> (<span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">PSA-AS</span>, <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">Secondary-init</span>), <strong><span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">Layla</span></strong> (<span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">iron deficiency anaemia</span>, <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">Primary-init</span>).</p>
</div>
<div class="sl-wrap">
