<div class="sl-actor" style="background:var(--platform);color:var(--platform-dark);border-color:var(--platform-dark);"><div class="sl-actor-portrait"><img alt="Priya" src="Assets/Personas/priya.png"/></div><div class="sl-actor-label"><span class="sl-actor-name">Priya</span>NHSE Platform</div></div>
<div class="sl-cell overlay"><span class="so-tag overlay-tag">Overlay · initiation</span><strong>I host the order.</strong>For <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="hiv">Self-init</span>: NHS App ordering surface, NHS Login identity verification, eligibility check against published criteria. For <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="psa-as">Secondary-init</span> / <span class="cfg-mark" data-config="ida">Primary-init</span>: I host the order entry from the clinical system. I route the order to Joe (supplier).</div>
