<div class="sl-cell overlay"><span class="so-tag overlay-tag">Overlay · supply chain</span><strong>I receive the order.</strong>I validate the address, allocate stock. Supplier model varies by configuration: all-inclusive (kit + lab + result through one supplier); split (logistics supplier + specialist lab as separate suppliers); pathology-led (lab anchors the chain).</div>
