  <div style="font-size:13.5px;color:#212B32;line-height:1.7;">Money flows commissioner-to-supplier under the call-off; the platform takes a small percent fee per completed test, not a margin on the kit. Payment triggers on a completed pathway &mdash; sample returned, lab processed, result delivered &mdash; so the supplier only earns on the service that actually happened. The lane exposes the framework as a marketplace rather than a wholesaler: the centre keeps the rails clean, runs the tariff treatment, and takes a transaction fee for the matchmaking. The commercial mechanics that set the rails sit upstream in Cap-4 of the Teamwork view; this lane is where those mechanics translate into live money movement.</div>
