  <div style="font-size:13.5px;color:#212B32;line-height:1.7;">The federated multi-controller model in motion: NHSE as the foundation controller, the commissioner controlling test purpose, the supplier as processor. DPIAs, DSAs and DPAs are inherited from framework templates and refreshed per configuration, with the IAO and IAA holding continuous oversight. The lane exposes that IG is structural, not incident-driven &mdash; the design choice that controllers are federated rather than joint determines the operational shape of every other lane downstream.</div>
